d\": 1927, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zohra_Bensemra\", \"score\": 0.9999999693654904, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Zohra Bensemra\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zohra_Bensemra\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zohra_Bensemra\"}, {\"begin\": 1952, \"end\": 1958, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Burton_Snowboards\", \"score\": 0.8726333154727054, \"rank\": 0.10324113772307947, \"text\": \"Burton\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Burton_Snowboards\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Burton_Snowboards\"}, {\"begin\": 1968, \"end\": 1980, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nine_Network\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.012450585054559e-17, \"text\": \"Nine Network\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nine_Network\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nine_Network\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"You sort of keep your head down and, try to just stay focused on the job at hand, but I am sure it'll sink in later on.\", \"from\": 1983, \"to\": 2103, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's amazing.\", \"from\": 2105, \"to\": 2119, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's a dream come true.\", \"from\": 2120, \"to\": 2143, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I do not know what happens when you get old, you get emotional all of a sudden.\\\"\", \"from\": 2144, \"to\": 2224, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Want more?Here's the full list of all our Olympics stories  Laura Collett, who had earlier led Great Britain to the team title, finished third on 23.10.\", \"from\": 2226, \"to\": 2378, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2286, \"end\": 2299, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laura_Collett\", \"score\": 0.9999948522782397, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Laura Collett\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laura_Collett\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laura_Collett\"}, {\"begin\": 2321, \"end\": 2334, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9998203576660647, \"rank\": 9.529158501316144e-05, \"text\": \"Great Britain\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Burton and Shadow Man only had their first competition together in March, when British owner Ben Hobday - believing he had no realistic chance of making the Olympics himself amid huge competition in the UK - loaned the horse for six months to his Australian pal.\", \"from\": 2380, \"to\": 2642, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2380, \"end\": 2386, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Burton_Snowboards\", \"score\": 0.8726333154727054, \"rank\": 0.10324113772307947, \"text\": \"Burton\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Burton_Snowboards\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Burton_Snowboards\"}, {\"begin\": 2391, \"end\": 2401, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trust_No_1\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.872366634773295e-14, \"text\": \"Shadow Man\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trust_No_1\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trust_No_1\"}, {\"begin\": 2583, \"end\": 2585, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9999998197618132, \"rank\": 1.7983851711964208e-07, \"text\": \"UK\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 2627, \"end\": 2637, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"score\": 0.9996372455882802, \"rank\": 0.0003602516506870229, \"text\": \"Australian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia